"title": "Using the Internet for Beat Development, Monitoring, and Data Finding",
"description": 'This text provides tips and resources for journalists on using the internet for beat development, monitoring, and data finding. It covers the importance of face-to-face interaction, developing contacts, and learning organizational structures. The text also discusses the use of online directories, dictionaries, and search engines. It emphasizes the importance of checking the source and credibility of information found online.',
